      </div>
      <div class="member exec">
        <img src="Images/Bharti.JPG" alt="Bharti">
        <div class="m-role">Executive Member</div>
        <div class="m-name">Bharti</div>
        <div class="m-bio">Dynamic educator &amp; HR professional, 10+ yrs. Dedicated to sustainable, transparent systems where residents are heard.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="member exec">
        <img src="Images/Surya Soman.JPG" alt="Surya Soman">
        <div class="m-role">Executive Member</div>
        <div class="m-name">Surya Soman</div>
